{"commentv2": 1, "number": 73, "id": 2434679, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Shashos", "body": "This fight is still buggy for hunters! Dismiss your pet before attacking Thorim or the entire fight bugs and he despawns, screwing up the encounter.", "date": "2016-10-25T22:31:19-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "thank you for the tip, ive tried fighting him like 5 times", "creationdate": "2017-01-07T18:49:19-06:00", "id": 1022390, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2434679, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DarkWolfDan", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He doesn't but on me. When I jump down off the podium, he turns his eyes on me, and that gives me time to call my pet.", "creationdate": "2018-11-09T22:00:54-06:00", "id": 1202008, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2434679, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "SilverDragon234", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 74, "id": 2462638, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Dreadalous", "body": "Just encountered a problem on this fight. Have done it a ton loads of times but on this occassion I dont know why but after i went into the room behind Thorim and jumped down i killed the mobs instead of [npc=32865] ....DUH mode I know. Anyway killing Thorim was not the problem. It seems Sara bugged and would not disappear and kept spamming frost bolts at me. Tried to use the teleporter but because I was in combat that wasn't possible. The only solution was to kill myself and hope the loot cache was still there when I got back. To kill yourself you need to go where [npc=32930]  was killed and you will notice a misty area around the balcony. Jump in and you will die and remove the aggro. The loot cache was still there and lootable.\r\n\r\nHope it helps.\r\n\r\nP.S. JUST kill [npc=32865] nothing else except the Iron Dwarves in the corridors as you're going up to him", "date": "2017-01-13T08:46:51-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Sara bugged on me a few times at 110, rather than die, I ran out of the area and ctrl+alt+del quit the game for 5 mins or so then logged back in. I was still in the same place only out of combat and the cache boxes were still there. It doesn't work if you quit while still in the room, you'll just log back in while still in combat.", "creationdate": "2018-05-31T08:55:32-05:00", "id": 1114563, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2462638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chewbarka", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This happened to me too. I shut the game and relogged and the chests were gone, but I had the loot in my mailbox!", "creationdate": "2019-03-23T07:36:53-05:00", "id": 1225487, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2462638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "AoifeNiav", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 75, "id": 2546439, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "153089", "body": "As of 7.3.5, the hard mode loot now drops from a chest that spawns next to the normal one. Make sure to loot it!", "date": "2018-01-17T16:50:51-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 76, "id": 2547361, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "rootbeerhead", "body": "Killed Thorim during my weekly Ulduar mount farm for the first time after patch 7.3.5, and saw there were two chests to loot. The mouseover referred to the regular chest as \"Cache of Storms\", and the other one was \"Heroic Cache of Storms\". I've run Ulduar since WotLK (70 runs now) and I have never noticed this second chest. Can't find it on wowhead, either, so either I've missed it every single time (embarrassing) or it was added with the Ulduar time walking update. I clear on 25 heroic every time.\r\n\r\nAlso, the port to Mimiron's lair at the entrance is gone, so no more skipping first boss.", "date": "2018-01-20T16:14:18-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The 2nd chest didn't spawn for me. I ran Ulduar on 10p Heroic. Is the 2nd chest exclusively for 25p Heroic?", "creationdate": "2020-08-24T13:13:17-05:00", "id": 1386022, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2547361, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lucilite", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 77, "id": 2562352, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Maravec", "body": "Walk in to Thorim's arena. There will be a few beasties to kill and Thorim will throw some stun attacks. Work your way to the left (as you're facing Thorim) to a lever near the wall. It will open a gate into the hallway, where some of the baddies might chase you. I faced more stun attacks from Thorim as well, probably because I didn't avoid the large, circular indentations in the floor of the hallway leading up to Thorim's back.\r\n\r\nOnce you attack Thorim, he will taunt you with some smacktalk and jump down into his arena, where he and his beasties will try to finish you off. Return the favor.", "date": "2018-04-11T12:11:18-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
