{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 473064, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "DrPancake", "body": "Wait, he [i]doesn't[/i] have a storm hammer? \r\n\r\n:(", "date": "2008-11-27T03:33:56-06:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Oh no, he does. You find out in a later quest chain that he threw it off of his tower in a fit of rage and sorrow. He asks you to help recover it.", "creationdate": "2009-01-11T00:27:57-06:00", "id": 71875, "rating": 29, "commentid": 473064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "65244", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "as you do.", "creationdate": "2009-04-30T07:26:06-05:00", "id": 94935, "rating": 16, "commentid": 473064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "261178", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Why help a Titan get his weapon back who got insane and slaughtered everything ? makes no sense :P", "creationdate": "2009-09-22T11:46:28-05:00", "id": 425606, "rating": 1, "commentid": 473064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "simis10", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Correction, he has a Thunder Rattle... Not an actual hammer - guess he's not old enough yet? (C'mon blizz, when you rip stuff off, at least do it well) >_>", "creationdate": "2012-07-04T07:15:51-05:00", "id": 554301, "rating": 2, "commentid": 473064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Swampax", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
