{"commentv2": 1, "number": 15, "id": 674979, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Darganon", "body": "One of the many servants of the Titans, Thorim and his brother Loken were tasked to protect what Ulduar holds [Yogg-saron].  Unfortunately, Loken was seduced by power promised by Yogg-Saron and killed Thorim's Wife, Sif, which drove him into a mad rage.  He lashed out to his allies and anger and hate and ultimately hurt his great friend, King Jokkum.", "date": "2009-04-13T09:21:57-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
