{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 832986, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "447260", "body": "To start doing the quests for Thorim, you have to complete a long quest chain that starts with They Took Our Men! in K3 (Gretchen Fizzlespark is the questgiver).\r\n\r\nThis chain will take you through a series of quests leading up to The Drakkensryd, which is one of the coolest mini-game style quests in Northrend imo. Once you're done with the requirements for this quest you have to talk to Thorim to complete it. Then you can begin doing quests for Thorim, which leads to unlocking the Sons of Hodir faction for your reputation grinding pleasure.", "date": "2009-09-05T20:59:14-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This quest chain is now available to grab from level 76 onwards.    Side-Note:  It indeed is one of the cooler mini-games, and [i]may/may not[/i] reference that one city in the USA where women outnumber the men 10+-to-1, and they have to advertise world-wide just to get husbands to live there.  An eligible-looking man traveling through there actually gets physically fought over if he eyeballs another woman...", "creationdate": "2011-02-13T23:06:40-06:00", "id": 224879, "rating": 0, "commentid": 832986, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "406368", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
