{"commentv2": 1, "number": 27, "id": 929094, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "424955", "body": "He now has voice commands for when you click on him and when you exit dialogue.", "date": "2009-12-26T13:33:05-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Like most npcs, he'll even get irritated when you click him a few times too many.  Quotes include but are not limited to: - \"I will CRUSH you!\" - \"BEGONE!\" - \"You call down the vengeance of THUNDER!\"  [small]They're oddly familiar to some quotes you'll hear when you encounter him in Ulduar. ;)[/small]", "creationdate": "2010-04-11T15:48:24-05:00", "id": 158564, "rating": 3, "commentid": 929094, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kciroj", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
