{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 1335327, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "406368", "body": "Quest-giver re-confirmed post-Cata, and at least a level 76 can grab it.  Thin possibility a 75 might, though only tried with a 74 party member and no luck.  Quest itself is given by [npc=29473] located at [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=29473#map]Goblin town K3[/url], who at level 77 starts you off with two quests, [quest=12843] and [quest=12844].  Both quests require you to fly (or ride a loooooooong way around) to get to the town way up above the frozen waterfall to the north of K3.  Completion of one of these quests lets you get [quest=12846], taking adventurers elsewhere along the chain.", "date": "2011-02-13T23:18:55-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-13T23:20:27-06:00", 2, "406368"]}
